{"tid":1294412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-07T18:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T18:54:06.000Z","uid":168214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a534be04171bde2551bd358aca6c3441bb119947","tid":1294412,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:49:00.000Z","msg":"如果個個禮拜遊行 我有一個擔憂<br />\n先唔講人數同鬥志 <br />\n假設真係咁做 又有足夠人數嘅時候<br />\n香港人最叻係咩 係善忘同麻目<br />\n最後變成個個禮拜遊行都係例行公事咁 行完就散 <br />\n就好似第一次有烈士犧牲 真係個個好大反應<br />\n但去到第四個呢 我唔多講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 支持遍地開花 十八區遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係十八區之後諗下和理非點樣行動升級<br />\n點樣俾最大壓力政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b814c7f8ca13f743e4607b9b22dbdcc5c7d563","tid":1294412,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"24d31afe42e422d9939cf1e1fda611d523128c46","tid":1294412,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:51:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ba5ecbb901113374bc77cd571dc8b7e539be0e07","tid":1294412,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:52:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3cfe37fdd47e6c66870aae37afdc14dbcc0be435","tid":1294412,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}